<h1> 
<p>申请须知</p>
<p>application notice</p>
</h1> 
<p>
1.申办人须提交有效身份证明文件，并从事稳定的正当职业。一人只能办理1张睿趣卡，通过认证后即申办成功，免费领取会员卡，填写同伴资料单人卡可升级为双人卡。
</p>
<p>
2.为了匹配您的需求，请您认真填写真实、完整的信息资料和调查问卷。我们承诺绝不会向任何第三方泄露涉及您的隐私信息。
</p>
<p>
3.会员卡开通后根据活跃程度晋级，获取更多福利。若连续12个月，未有任何参与记录，会员卡将自动失效。
</p>
<p>
4.密切关注星乐趴微信公众号（lovelyparty520），了解最新动态、活动公告和会员专属福利，预约报名要参加的活动和项目。预约成功后，请关注电子邮件、手机短信或电话通知，及时回复确认，以免错过活动。
</p>
<p>
5.睿趣卡只限本人使用，不得转借他人，申请双人卡后，可与指定对象一起使用。
</p>
<p>
6.若不慎遗失睿趣卡或人为损坏无法使用时，您可凭本人有效身份证至会员服务中心办理补卡手续，补卡后的新卡沿用原卡的有效期和有效积分，原卡即被注销。补卡工本费：10元。
</p>
<p>
7.若信息资料发生变更，请及时凭本人有效身份证至会员服务中心办理资料变更手续，以便我们能更好地为您服务。
</p>
<p>
8.申办星乐趴睿趣卡均视为理解并接受本须知。成功申办后，参加活动时须举止文明，服从管理，不得影响公共秩序与安全，否则星乐趴有权取消其会员资格。
</p>
<p>
1.Applicant should show us your ID card and employment certificate. One person corresponds  to only one Yohoo Smart Card, and you can have VIP card free after verification.
</p>
<p>
2.In order to satisfy your needs precisely, please provide the real, complete information and questionnaire. We promise never to spread your information to the third part.
</p>
<p>
3.Card is originally general level ; it can offer you more privileges after activation and upgrading. If there is no record on your card in 12 consecutive months, your card will be canceled automatically.
</p>
<p>
4.Follow the Starring Lovely Party’s Wechat: lovelyparty520 to get the latest announcement, notice and VIP activities and more details. You are also able to make an appointment; please focus on your E-mail, message and phone-call when appoint successfully. Please check it timely in case of missing.
</p>
<p>
5.Yohoo Smart Card can only be used by yourself. It cannot be lend to others, but it can be used with your appointed friend after upgrading to Double Card.
</p>
<p>
6.If you lost your Yohoo Smart Card or the card is damaged artificially, you can go to the VIP Service Center for the procedure. Your VIP points will be transferred to the new card, and the former card will be canceled. The charge for the card procedure is 10 yuan.
</p>
<p>
7.If there is something change on the information, please go to the VIP Service Center to alter the information timely for the better service.   
</p>
<P>
8.Applying for the Yohoo Smart Card is regarded as understanding and agreeing on this notice. When you participates in activities, you should behave politely, obey the management and not damage public order and safety. Or you’ll be canceled the VIP qualification.
</P>
